ons to render the scheme\nfeasible in the upcoming Extreme Light Infrastructure (ELI) laser facility.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Feb 2012 14:46:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-04"}
